This extension will do the tasks:
 - Import data of  product from Aliexpress to Prestashop module
 - Setting display method shipping, estimated time of delivery product. Convert money automatically of  product 
- Automatically fullfill your order on Aliexpress
- Get tracking code and status order from Aliexpress
- Auto update product's data Aliexpress
- Auto get ID Order when payment successfully
- And more features
